  <brief_title>Efficacy Evaluation Of Great Occipital Nerve Electrical Stimulation On Rebound Headache</brief_title>
  <official_title>EFFICACY EVALUATION OF GREAT OCCIPITAL NERVE ELECTRICAL STIMULATION ON REBOUND HEADACHE AFTER WITHDRAWAL IN MEDICATION OVERUSE HEADACHE OCCURING IN MIGRAINE PATIENTS (SENGO-CAM Study)</official_title>
